asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Scoop McDoobigle
description:
Born Scotland 1944, ran away to sea at 13 , after an early career as a pirate in Indonesia he settled in New Orleans working as a debt collector.

Drafted Vietnam War 1967, Scoop discovered he'd rather shoot pictures than bunnies and a career as a legendary war photographer was born. Covered every major conflict since and started more than a few minor ones. 

Hell raiser, raconteur, best selling author of "Guns, Carrots and Steel - A life under fire and under ground" . Married 5 times, divorced 3, children, he's lost count.... Available for public speaking

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: CRIMSON aka RED ALERT
description: CRIMSON, code name RED ALERT, is the leader of an elite team of specially trained FLUFs known as E. A. R. S, Elite Auxiliary Rabbit Squad, whose mission is to protect FLUF World from external threats. Trained in all forms of martial arts and weaponry, a polymath whose intellect ranks as one of the most brilliant minds in FLUF World, CRIMSON has lead his elite team of guardians in epic battles and has mitigated countless catastrophes that threatened all of FLUFdom. CRIMSONs civilian identity is of an iconic music artist who formed the legendary rock band Crimson Hare, pioneering the Post Flunk movement. Rumor has it that CRIMSONs ancestry can be traced back to an ancient clan of warriors known as The REDS. Elder FLUFs  recall tales of how REDS were once BLU FLUFs who transformed during an event called First Impact, when a meteor from the red planet Mars hit Earth millions of years ago. The fur of BLU FLUFs exposed to mysterious frequencies emanating from the meteor turned red. This also changed their biology, making REDS more sensitive to vibration, which lead to the evolutionary inherent characteristics of FLUFs reacting positively to music through shaking.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
